cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

This paper involves the use of robotics, computer vision, and machine learning techniques to enable cloud-edge hybrid control of a dynamic self-balancing robot. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also heavily relies on computer vision techniques such as image-based visual servoing and apriltag recognition, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). The use of a smart edge device and the need for real-time control and communication suggest that it could also belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also mentions the use of deep-learning recognition systems, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
